        "created_at": "2024-03-13T09:49:43.472Z",
        "cooked": "<p>While using the Signal for voice calls, I’ve encountered an issue where the display fails to turn off even when the phone is placed close to my ear. This occurrence is inconsistent with the behavior observed in other call applications like Phone and WhatsApp, where the screen automatically shuts off during calls. This discrepancy poses the risk of accidental clicks, interruptions, or disconnections during calls.</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 4,
        "updated_at": "2024-03-14T04:07:58.107Z",
